== Notes == {{Notelist |refs = <ref name="VMware ESX Server">Can run a guest OS without modifying it, and hence is generally able to run any OS that could run on a physical machine the VM simulates.</ref> <ref name="vmware8">Version 3.0.0 and earlier allowed 8 cores.</ref> }}
